---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { useTranslations } from "@/i18n/ui";
const t = useTranslations("en");
---
<BaseLayout title={t("nav.about")}>
  <article class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-5 pt-16 pb-16">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-6xl leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-6">About</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>Welcome to <strong>ZoroTreeking</strong>. A personal site where I keep notes and records across four interests:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>AI Learning</strong> — paper notes, tool experiments, technical thoughts</li>
        <li><strong>Investment</strong> — account reviews and monthly records (personal learning log, not investment advice)</li>
        <li><strong>Photography</strong> — albums organized by theme, location and year</li>
        <li><strong>Hiking</strong> — route tracks, elevation profiles, trip logs</li>
      </ul>
      <p>All content is personal, original or curated. Feel free to leave a comment.</p>
      <hr />
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mt-10 mb-4">Compliance</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">This is a <strong>non-commercial personal site</strong>: no commerce, no public account registration, no third-party content uploads. The AI chat widget is for study and conversation only — user input is screened by a keyword filter before being forwarded to the LLM. Like / pageview tracking stores only an IP+UA hash fingerprint and a timestamp; no phone numbers, email addresses or real names are collected.</p>
      <ul class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
        <li><strong>ICP filing</strong>: <a href="https://beian.miit.gov.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">沪 ICP 备 2026021578 号-1</a></li>
        <li><strong>Site operator / Security officer</strong>: Zoro (the owner)</li>
        <li><strong>Abuse / complaint email</strong>: <a href="mailto:1437066318@qq.com">1437066318@qq.com</a> (response within 48 hours)</li>
        <li><strong>Log retention</strong>: access logs and interaction records are kept ≥ 6 months and provided to regulators / law enforcement upon lawful request</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Full complaint procedure on the <a href="/en/contact">Contact page</a>. Open-sourced on <a href="https://github.com/lzf00/zorotreeking">GitHub</a>, built with Astro 4, deployed automatically.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
